Currently Squid 6.12 from Debian cannot be build on Ubuntu 24.04 - there is an error https://www.mail-archive.com/debian-bugs-dist@lists.debian.org/msg1998244.html

One way to still build is to disable the link optimization as in rules.patch

We need to wait till upstream fixes it.
For now we do NOT move web safety to Ubuntu 24.04 as base platform.



